<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Booking Email Failure</title>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap');
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
        color: #e74c3c;
        text-align: center;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .info {
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
        padding: 15px;
        border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #999;
      }
      footer h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #333;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>⚠️ Failed to Send Confirmation Email</h1>
      <p>Dear Admin,</p>
      <p>We attempted to send a booking confirmation email to the customer below, but the operation failed.</p>

      <div class="info">
        <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> {{bookingId}}</p>
        <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{fullName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> {{phoneNumber}}</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{time}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>Please investigate the issue or attempt to confirm manually.</p>

      <footer>
        <h2>{{businessName}}</h2>
        <p>&copy; {{year}} {{businessName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
